1.	Open aws, search for IAM service
2.	On left side search for “Roles” inside Access Management
3.	Click on “Create Role” button on left top side
4.	Choose `Trusted Entity Type` & `Use Case` that suits you.
5.	In add permission, select which policy you wanna add then click on Next button
6.	Give proper name, description and edited trusted entity if wanna change something
7.	Click on Create role button
